13:
Hello there! Lovely weather we're
having! Are you stuck without an
umbrella?
17:
Yes... It is proving to be quite an
issue.
21:
I am supposed to meet my friends,
but I cannot leave like this.
25:
Then why don't we share mine? We
can splishy-splash all the way to
your friends together!
34: Of course! I'm Phi Nonoa, by the way!
37:
Thank you, and it is nice to meet
you, Nonoa. My name is Stella.
41:
Nice to meet you too! Now, shall we
plippity-plop along?
45:
Hehe, do you hear that? I just looove
the sound of raindrops
drippity-dropping on my umbrella!
51: It is indeed a nice sound.
55:
Hehe, right? Now then, we're off!
Splishy-splash!
59:
Doesn't look like it's going to let up
any time soon... I hope Stella's
staying dry...
63: Hello! Are you Alk and Light?
66:
This is Nonoa. She shared her
umbrella with me on the way here.
69:
Hehe, I'm glad you got to find your
friends!
72:
Well then, I'll just plippity-plop along!
See you around!
76:
Wait. Would you perhaps like to take
a walk with us?
81:
Really? I'd love to! I'd be happier
than a frog in rain!
84:
Come on, you two, get under this
umbrella!
88:
I-I don't believe we will all fit under
there...
92:
Well, in that case, you three can use
the umbrella, and I'll make do with
my raincoat!
102:
Phi Nonoa's Rainy Day Tour, now
departing!
108:
You know... Walking around in the
rain felt pretty nice!
112: Didn't it? I just looove rainy walks!
115:
The perfect weather, a leisurely
stroll, and new friends? Today must
be my lucky day!
118:
Yo, Nonoa! Looks like someone's in a
good mood again today.
121:
Of course I am! Rainy days are my
absolute favorite!
123:
Haha! Good to hear! Anyway, can't
wait to go on some quests with you
again sometime!
126:
From that exchange... Are we to
assume you are also an adventurer?
129:
Yup! I've joined all sorts of parties!
Everyone is super-duper nice!
134:
I'm sure they feel the same way
about you.
138:
Y-you think so? I sure hope you're
right! Hehe.
142: Looks like the rain finally let up.
146:
It sure did. But you know what? The
cool air after a shower always feels
extra nice!
149:
Anyway, thanks for hanging out with
me today! See ya—
152:
Nonoa! I've been looking all over for
you!
154:
Miss Innkeeper? I was just on my
way back now. What's wrong?
156:
It's about your reservation... One of
the trainees canceled it by mistake!
158:
By the time I noticed, we had
already filled your room and every
other... I asked the other inns if they
had a room for you, but... I'm so sorry!
161:
Come on, turn that frown upside
down! I'll be fine! Make sure the
trainee knows I'm not mad either,
okay?
165:
You may say it's fine, but... Do you
have a place to stay?
169:
Nope! But that's okay. I'm an
adventurer, so I'll be fine roughing it
in the woods for the night!
174:
Would you like to stay with us
instead?
181:
Whoooa! Who would've thought
such a pretty place was just a hop
and a skip away!
188:
Thank you! Hehe, so not only did I
make new friends, but I found a
whole new town too!
192: Rainy days really are my lucky days!
